item.title: My god
item.dc:creator: @usman555 usman555
item.description:
@usman555 wrote:

I don’t know anybody in these forums that can read a class file.

If someone were to help you and make yourself an owner, that’d be done and over with. But who makes a server just to make themselves an owner? You’ll ask for more help and you won’t know a single thing about 711s. Every time you want to make a change, you’ll have to ask the forums for help and we all know that this forum lacks people that know about 711s.

My advice is to simply stick to a lower revision, something easy to understand yet pushing you towards understanding 711s so you won’t have to be spoonfed.

Read full topic
